クラス CriterionOptimumComputer<S extends IPBSolver>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sat4j.pb.multiobjective.CriterionOptimumComputer<S>
  • 型パラメータ:
    S - Subsolvers type

    public class CriterionOptimumComputer<S extends IPBSolver>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used to compute optimal values for each criteria for a given problem. Computation is parallelized.
